-- Google Asks Appeals Court to Void Suit as Class Action
-- B y   D o n   J e f f r e y
-- 2013-05-08T15:13:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-08/google-asks-appeals-court-to-void-suit-as-class-action.html
Google Inc. (GOOG)  asked an appeals court to
reject class-action status for a lawsuit over digital books that
a company lawyer said includes a request for more than
$3 billion in damages.  To contact the reporter on this story:
